Exploring and wrangling

data <- tt$babynames %>% 
  filter(year == 2017) %>% 
  group_by(name, sex) %>% 
  summarise(n = sum(n)) %>% 
  mutate(
    sex = case_when(
      sex == 'M' ~ 'BOYS',
      TRUE       ~ 'GIRLS')
    )
